<div id='introduction'>

  <div class='options-container'>
    <ul class='list-inline'>
      <li>
        <%= button_tag type: 'button', disabled: true, id: 'take_test' do %>
          <%= image_tag 'take_the_test.png', class: 'take-test-img' %>
        <% end %>
        <p class='take-test-text'>Take the Test!!</p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <%= link_to result_page_path, data: {no_turbolink: true} do %>
          <%= image_tag 'view_results.png', width: '65%', id: 'view_results_link' %>
        <% end %>
        <p class='view-result-text'>View Results</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>SpeedUp San Jose identifies the real life internet speed our residents experience. We need your help to learn which neighborhoods consistently have slow internet connections. All you have to do is answer a couple of questions and conduct a speed test.</p>
  <p>We value your privacy, and will not collect any personal information. We will incorporate your general location in the aggregate data.</p>
  <p>Once the testing period is over, we will have a more complete picture of internet speeds in every part of the city. From there we can take steps to ensure all San Jose residents have access to quality, high-speed internet.</p>

  <%= render partial: 'shared/info_link' %>

  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-lg-7 col-xs-11 col-sm-9 col-centered'>
      <div class='partnerLogos'>
        <p>Brought to you by:</p>

        <div class='row'>
          <%= link_to image_tag('companyLogos/logo1.png'), '#' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='col-lg-12 col-xs-12 col-sm-12'>
      <div class='google-section'><div id='google_translate_element'></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
